# =============================================
# 安装说明 (README)
# =============================================
# 克隆此仓库后，需要手动安装以下包：
#
# 1. ChatdollKit:
#    - 下载: ChatdollKit_0.8.15.unitypackage
#    - 或从 GitHub: https://github.com/uezo/ChatdollKit
#
# 2. VRM 1.0:
#    - 下载: VRM-0.130.1_c721.unitypackage
#    - 或从 GitHub: https://github.com/vrm-c/UniVRM
#
# 3. uLipSync:
#    - 下载: uLipSync-v3.1.4-with-Samples.unitypackage
#    - 或从 GitHub: https://github.com/hecomi/uLipSync
#
# 4. UniTask:
#    - 下载: UniTask.2.5.10.unitypackage
#    - 或从 GitHub: https://github.com/Cysharp/UniTask
#
# 5. AnimeGirlIdleAnimations_free:
#    - 从 Unity Asset Store 下载
#
# 安装顺序建议: UniTask → VRM → ChatdollKit → uLipSync → 动画包
#
# 安装后在 Project Settings > Player > Scripting Define Symbols 添加:
# USE_VRM10

